snippet.title: Skully - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Skully is a charming platforming adventure that's available now on Nintendo Switch. Roll into the action with three forms that aid in overcoming environmental obstacles, hop over platforms and danger as a boney hero, and save the island from a familial feud!

Available Now: https://nintendo.com/games/detail/skully-switch/
